item.title: CVE-2024-25946|2024-07-16T17:02:35.177Z -- dell -- virtual%20appliance%20%28vapp%29%20manager
item.description: Dell vApp Manager, versions prior to 9.2.4.9 contain a Command Injection Vulnerability. An authorized attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability leading to an execution of an inserted command. Dell recommends customers to upgrade at the earliest opportunity.
